WEBVTT

00:05:29.080 --> 00:05:32.216
we're often concerned
with performing at our best,

00:05:32.240 --> 00:05:35.696
and as a result we try and control
what we're doing

00:05:35.720 --> 00:05:38.096
to force the best performance.

00:05:38.120 --> 00:05:40.760
The end result
is that we actually screw up.

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.376
In basketball,

00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:47.640
the term "unconscious" is used
to describe a shooter who can't miss.

00:05:49.000 --> 00:05:53.016
And San Antonio Spurs star
Tim Duncan has said,

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:56.896
"When you have to stop and think,
that's when you mess up."

00:05:56.920 --> 00:06:00.656
